testBody: public static boolean test() throws Throwable {java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D rec = new java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D.Double(10, 20, 10, 2);java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D target = new java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D.Double(16, 21, 10, 2);java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D result = translate(rec, 6, 1);return (target.equals(result));}
